[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Inspecting GitUtil settings**\n\nI think GitUtil settings might read from /.scm/git-settings.xml, but I could use some guidance on that. I want to set the user.home temporarily to avoid any weird issues with host settings. If I'm constructing command line tests, it’s reading user home and the default Git setup. In native tests, maybe the user.home is the repo, but I’m not sure it’s necessary. I should check the default settings of GitUtil and get the commons jar too.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_02b75550e3383ed0016a2a5ed88b348194b4a5e2c113c4acb4\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKl7bVae_lC_I6vbrcsjQWkUyLRBM9f-ulfvjz2SNkKVwMkVjmpCvML7Wod8LrzajyAVVckvjIrWXduxyiF1pljxz5-ruWiQgjAgcBUbgxLOi0Lq7sSZl-2SuyYJPwLrtYAUhxljiNOOQMWBitRLCeKF9Q_v2rnu7Axx2J75aWOR7vF-Cx00leeMDYOmY_LX7hRWOXKsB5t_U61vMlrYzt3kGRG99Oy4xUQdQCZJ7GCLZ0-96UbHCX3nF7yzf4w9EqEJ36yrXJDjM0fLGUtfMo1G28AlItx8pEVZt0AJJ12SlBjRGkqWWmQR5H-oncG0_TYPVt4NbicEgojh3AMylyrDPftkwEMzMwbbvU1F922i9X3-bU6ugvHWEqGhac7Jpgdoem6b3PCaPoC1VJ_kpkqSQcBFinFyEoyLKbdIaALP4z5XU3zq3-PkzRD11Th3PZdtuC_QuuQfhRl5HHsPxy5qCglmmlC5_6Egfpx4vXScEy0z7tQ3yfCgYk3m9Sc5QfAt6i72pXp2Uz5vRBxAZIuy4HoCPlXQzXIBW8BNcrqlWZ9ULXcHoeBH7BblTfP9SUpYNqD6jZdazvtD70_pNtsvnUgtp0-7-Ta4-i36zNmY5XxwPhG47yDzdBkrs6XYcMEIS1fXYeBBID4cvI2scsDa2z8abadQ2T1HATy7Az6anSyX0-anQu3KkglFswbb0BBpf0fn6uTFNpJBcS6ZRYspq8Y1QPsh9UftP6-uZuMG38CrUr7H5Cfyz8wua8xgAtf5mc4vpTbUGZ0UDLYWT9ND1vQ7tSEoiFLu9LnREyroQpJp3Jd_HtIdFBJkcONK1aLISZC6tBNyAW0niudLgUlqCfXUjiseJQ_gGJiIpSsyxzTxTbhYkoESmOJOKpdB2XsAT2AvQhQwzQbecvLf5MERoYKdoIDDz8KL0xq0Pv0JCVrJTAc7YiehAoJT0I8bK2FKEzO2u0513XP8KNNgoln7fZm3azUd7kXDjnunjangAEMThDG6T5FmPIEbHnv-0B9_-qQ6VgXAfZY-QL7iGEkrRUWdwVyDTWqLtkvJVABYUnuBGwnT2McwpAqN7vbeqBuVfvzuXtxq3IiaJhEVZjthhDl0RBhuScyrvsbZTDtz95abBTkYfwYCSNZCtUXz-7VLG-0c_edgvSr61TYX0BpCFsrucvObRnhpiFQG5EVJVM5dk2gMCKWDHd0rjtErbQb6_OdNZgby2APLRZzHHLrA8wqx3OXK4_OFXe3AzRq4